// Session scopes:
// - per-sender: Each sender gets their own session (default)
// - per-channel: All users in a channel share one session
// - per-group: All users in a group share one session
//
// DM scopes:
// - main: All DMs collapse to one main session (default)
// - per-peer: Each DM peer gets separate session
// - per-channel-peer: Separate sessions per channel+peer
// - per-account-channel-peer: Separate sessions per account+channel+peer
